parameters:
\SE[2]Oh my... Looks like I forgot to buy eggs. \SE[8]This
is troublesome, what should I do...?

\SM[double]\SE[22]Ah, then I'll go buy them. \SE[21]I'll
quickly take care of it.

\SE[52]No, it's no good...! \SE[53]Being alone at this
time... It's already late at night...
\SE[2]Hmm... I also want to go for a walk...

\SE[37]Fine... I got it. \SE[0]Make sure you don't take too
long, okay?
\SE[21] I wonder if this is what 'happiness' feels like...
\SE[37]It's not... The eggs are still missing.

\SE[2]Laura and the others, should we start heading back
soon? I hope the food doesn't get cold...

\SE[49]Both of you... hurry up and come back...
\SE[58]Lunaroa- san is feeling lonely, you know...?

\SE[2]... I wonder who it could be? \ I'm sorry, but I don't
accept visitors late at night.
Here they come... Everyone, get ready...!!

\SE[47]They came into our house without any reservation...
\!\SE[58]...I got a little angry.

When I look at the flames, my heart becomes calm... The
flames here are the most comforting.
